k > 1
\begin{align} D &=\dfrac{b^{k+1}}{b(k+1)}-\left(\frac{b}{2}\right)^k\\ &=\dfrac{b^{k}}{k+1}-\frac{b^k}{2^k}\\ &=b^{k}\left(\dfrac{1}{k+1}-\dfrac{1}{2^k}\right)\\ &> 0\\ \end{align} 
