4(1+x+x^2) > 3(1+2x+x^2)
1 - 2x + x^2 > 0
k
1+x
\begin{align} (k+1)(1+x)^{k+1} &< 2^k(1+x)\sum_{i=0}^k x^i \\ &= 2^k\left(\sum_{i=0}^k x^i+\sum_{i=0}^k x^{i+1}\right) \\ &= 2^k\left(\sum_{i=0}^k x^i+\sum_{i=1}^{k+1} x^{i}\right) \\ &= 2^k\left(1+x^{k+1}+2\sum_{i=1}^k x^i\right) \\ &= 2^k\left(-1-x^{k+1}+2\sum_{i=0}^{k+1} x^i\right) \\ &= -2^k(1+x^{k+1})+2^{k+1}\sum_{i=0}^{k+1} x^i \\ \end{align} 
